issue.title: Better UI for filter on empty string in query builder

comment.body:
> Hi SigNoz team, just need a small clarification. In the search filter, after selecting the operators, is it expected to list options with one of them being empty string with quotes. like in the below snapshot, instead of <component = > the first option has to be <component = ' ' >
> 
> ![Screenshot from 2023-10-27 00-25-18](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/64725924/278449042-86f9bd4c-674a-4db3-a265-1f75c9988a21.png)

Yes @joemiltonm, currently it's expected.
